## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of the influence of the environment on architecture. The findings are limited to the perspectives and data available in the sources reviewed. Further research, including field studies and expert interviews, could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic. Additionally, the dynamic nature of architectural practices means that new trends and technologies may influence future developments in this field.